<ul>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://sites.google.com/site/fernwebsite">The Foresight, Education &amp; Research Network "FERN" is a global community of foresight students, alumni, faculty, employers, and advocates of graduate foresight education, employment, and research.</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.globalforesight.org">Global Foresight Org lists communities, degree programs, courses, people, employers, organizations, and educational materials that help advance our global foresight culture. It can be edited by anyone who wants to help.</a></li>
</ul>
